tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE mood_behavior_data (
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  therapist_id UUID,
  patient_id UUID,
  session_date DATE,
  mood_score INT,
  behavior_description VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE therapy_sessions (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    therapist_id UUID,
    patient_id UUID,
    session_date DATE,
    session_duration INTERVAL,
    mood_rating INTEGER,
    behavior_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE therapists (
    therapist_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    therapist_name VARCHAR(255),
    specialization VARCHAR(255),
    consultant BOOLEAN,
    license_number VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255),
    date_of_birth DATE,
    gender CHAR(1),
    contact_number VARCHAR(20),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    address TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE TherapySession (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  therapist_id INT,
  patient_id INT,
  session_date DATE,
  session_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE MoodFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  mood_score INT,
  mood_description TEXT,
  mood_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Session (session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 therapist_id UUID,
 date TIMESTAMP,
 client_id UUID,
 mood VARCHAR,
 behavior VARCHAR);

CREATE TABLE Therapist (therapist_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR,
 email VARCHAR,
 phone_number VARCHAR);

CREATE TABLE Client (client_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR,
 email VARCHAR,
 age INT,
 gender VARCHAR);
